  "script": [
    {
      "start": 0.0,
      "end": 5.6,
      "text": "우리 0810님께 굿모닝 팝 3개월 구독권 보내드리겠습니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 5.6,
      "end": 7.4,
      "text": "힘내라 힘!"
    },
    {
      "start": 7.78,
      "end": 10.34,
      "text": "GMP와 함께 시작하는 에너지 넘치는 하루"
    },
    {
      "start": 10.34,
      "end": 13.16,
      "text": "GMP로 영어 실력 업! 에너지도 업!"
    },
    {
      "start": 13.72,
      "end": 17.94,
      "text": "오늘은 맛있는 커피와 샌드위치로 든든하게 하루를 시작해보세요"
    },
    {
      "start": 17.94,
      "end": 22.06,
      "text": "지금 바로 메시지 보내주시면 총 5분 뽑아서"
    },
    {
      "start": 22.06,
      "end": 25.32,
      "text": "커피 앤 샌드위치 모바일 쿠폰 보내드립니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 25.32,
      "end": 31.0,
      "text": "단문 50원과 장문 100원에 추가요금이 부과되는 KBS 쿨에페 문자 샵 8910"
    },
    {
      "start": 31.0,
      "end": 34.9,
      "text": "또는 KBS 2라디오 문자 샵 1061로 보내주시거나"
    },
    {
      "start": 34.9,
      "end": 39.16,
      "text": "무료인 KBS 애플리케이션 콩 또는 KBS 플러스로 참여해주세요"
    },
    {
      "start": 39.16,
      "end": 52.32,
      "text": "임여섯 시 조정현의 굿모닝 팝"
    },
    {
      "start": 52.32,
      "end": 56.72,
      "text": "해봐요 굿모닝"
    },
    {
      "start": 56.72,
      "end": 60.27,
      "text": "조정현의 굿모닝"
    },
    {
      "start": 60.27,
      "end": 65.96,
      "text": "조정현의 굿모닝 팝"
    },
    {
      "start": 65.96,
      "end": 81.08,
      "text": "English"
    },
    {
      "start": 81.08,
      "end": 100.61,
      "text": "Morning Theater, Screen English Time"
    },
    {
      "start": 100.61,
      "end": 102.25,
      "text": "4월에 함께하는 영화는"
    },
    {
      "start": 102.25,
      "end": 104.57,
      "text": "Katak, The Brave Beluga"
    },
    {
      "start": 104.57,
      "end": 107.75,
      "text": "용감한 돌고래 멜로와 바닷속 친구들"
    },
    {
      "start": 107.75,
      "end": 112.57,
      "text": "Embarking on a Grand Adventure to Uncover Underwater Legends"
    },
    {
      "start": 112.57,
      "end": 115.87,
      "text": "오늘따라 목소리가 더욱더 멋지신데요"
    },
    {
      "start": 115.87,
      "end": 116.71,
      "text": "Thank you very much"
    },
    {
      "start": 116.71,
      "end": 117.99,
      "text": "Yeah, 좋습니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 117.99,
      "end": 118.89,
      "text": "It's good to hear that"
    },
    {
      "start": 118.89,
      "end": 120.91,
      "text": "You have a beautiful voice yourself"
    },
    {
      "start": 120.91,
      "end": 125.91,
      "text": "수중 전설적인 대상을 밝히기 위해"
    },
    {
      "start": 125.91,
      "end": 127.33,
      "text": "그러니까 찾아내기 위해서"
    },
    {
      "start": 127.33,
      "end": 131.43,
      "text": "이제 대모험에 착수하게 되는 이야기죠"
    },
    {
      "start": 131.43,
      "end": 132.59,
      "text": "Yeah, that's correct"
    },
    {
      "start": 132.59,
      "end": 137.13,
      "text": "Our little katak is about to go on a big adventure"
    },
    {
      "start": 137.13,
      "end": 139.53,
      "text": "Yeah, 이보현님께서요"
    },
    {
      "start": 139.53,
      "end": 142.89,
      "text": "출근 준비 중인데 귀 활짝 열고 듣고 있어요"
    },
    {
      "start": 142.89,
      "end": 145.01,
      "text": "크리스쌤 오늘도 굿모닝입니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 145.01,
      "end": 146.41,
      "text": "아, 좋습니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 146.41,
      "end": 146.91,
      "text": "네"
    },
    {
      "start": 146.91,
      "end": 148.55,
      "text": "닦고 계시는 분들"
    },
    {
      "start": 148.55,
      "end": 149.65,
      "text": "이제 열고"
    },
    {
      "start": 149.65,
      "end": 152.41,
      "text": "네, 귀를 활짝 열어주시면 되겠습니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 152.41,
      "end": 153.35,
      "text": "Open those ears"
    },
    {
      "start": 153.35,
      "end": 154.67,
      "text": "Listen carefully"
    },
    {
      "start": 154.67,
      "end": 156.19,
      "text": "And stay tuned"
    },
    {
      "start": 156.19,
      "end": 156.83,
      "text": "알겠습니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 156.83,
      "end": 160.19,
      "text": "자, 우리 벨루가들을 우리가 계속해서 보고 있는데"
    },
    {
      "start": 160.19,
      "end": 162.23,
      "text": "이 동물적으로 봤을 때"
    },
    {
      "start": 162.23,
      "end": 165.41,
      "text": "벨루가스들이 are endangered animals잖아요"
    },
    {
      "start": 165.41,
      "end": 166.87,
      "text": "Oh, yeah, they were"
    },
    {
      "start": 166.87,
      "end": 168.61,
      "text": "And they have been"
    },
    {
      "start": 168.61,
      "end": 171.93,
      "text": "Mostly they live in the Arctic"
    },
    {
      "start": 171.93,
      "end": 172.91,
      "text": "Yes"
    },
    {
      "start": 172.91,
      "end": 176.25,
      "text": "They live in Arctic and sub-Arctic waters"
    },
    {
      "start": 176.25,
      "end": 178.85,
      "text": "Those waters are very, very cold"
    },
    {
      "start": 178.85,
      "end": 180.25,
      "text": "And full of ice"
    },
    {
      "start": 180.25,
      "end": 180.79,
      "text": "그렇죠"
    },
    {
      "start": 180.79,
      "end": 182.63,
      "text": "So, as we mentioned, they can survive"
    },
    {
      "start": 182.63,
      "end": 184.05,
      "text": "In super cold waters"
    },
    {
      "start": 184.05,
      "end": 185.51,
      "text": "그런데 문제는"
    },
    {
      "start": 185.51,
      "end": 188.13,
      "text": "Even glaciers have been melting"
    },
    {
      "start": 188.13,
      "end": 189.31,
      "text": "They have"
    },
    {
      "start": 189.31,
      "end": 190.69,
      "text": "They've been melting"
    },
    {
      "start": 190.69,
      "end": 194.29,
      "text": "Also, people like to, you know, spill chemicals"
    },
    {
      "start": 194.29,
      "end": 195.65,
      "text": "They don't like to"
    },
    {
      "start": 195.65,
      "end": 197.15,
      "text": "But sometimes accidents happen"
    },
    {
      "start": 197.15,
      "end": 197.79,
      "text": "Oh, 맞아요"
    },
    {
      "start": 197.79,
      "end": 199.93,
      "text": "And that has caused a lot of trauma"
    },
    {
      "start": 199.93,
      "end": 202.55,
      "text": "And destruction to their environment"
    },
    {
      "start": 202.55,
      "end": 203.11,
      "text": "그렇죠"
    },
    {
      "start": 203.11,
      "end": 204.41,
      "text": "So, they were considered"
    },
    {
      "start": 204.41,
      "end": 206.63,
      "text": "Beluga whales were considered vulnerable"
    },
    {
      "start": 206.63,
      "end": 207.11,
      "text": "Oh"
    },
    {
      "start": 207.11,
      "end": 208.51,
      "text": "In 1996"
    },
    {
      "start": 208.51,
      "end": 209.17,
      "text": "Uh-huh"
    },
    {
      "start": 209.17,
      "end": 211.37,
      "text": "Then their status improved"
    },
    {
      "start": 211.37,
      "end": 211.89,
      "text": "Uh-huh"
    },
    {
      "start": 211.89,
      "end": 213.15,
      "text": "To near threatened"
    },
    {
      "start": 213.15,
      "end": 213.71,
      "text": "Uh-huh"
    },
    {
      "start": 213.71,
      "end": 214.75,
      "text": "Oh, sorry, did not improve it"
    },
    {
      "start": 214.75,
      "end": 215.57,
      "text": "It 떨어졌어"
    },
    {
      "start": 215.57,
      "end": 215.95,
      "text": "Ah"
    },
    {
      "start": 215.95,
      "end": 217.65,
      "text": "They got even more endangered"
    },
    {
      "start": 217.65,
      "end": 218.11,
      "text": "네"
    },
    {
      "start": 218.11,
      "end": 219.89,
      "text": "Near threatened in 2008"
    },
    {
      "start": 219.89,
      "end": 220.57,
      "text": "Uh-huh"
    },
    {
      "start": 220.57,
      "end": 222.05,
      "text": "But then they made a recovery"
    },
    {
      "start": 222.05,
      "end": 223.65,
      "text": "In 2017"
    },
    {
      "start": 223.65,
      "end": 226.05,
      "text": "They were declared as"
    },
    {
      "start": 226.05,
      "end": 227.79,
      "text": "Not endangered"
    },
    {
      "start": 227.79,
      "end": 228.23,
      "text": "Uh-huh"
    },
    {
      "start": 228.23,
      "end": 230.11,
      "text": "Least concern status"
    },
    {
      "start": 230.11,
      "end": 230.55,
      "text": "Uh-huh"
    },
    {
      "start": 230.55,
      "end": 232.45,
      "text": "But actually, in the United States"
    },
    {
      "start": 232.45,
      "end": 232.83,
      "text": "Uh-huh"
    },
    {
      "start": 232.83,
      "end": 235.07,
      "text": "Beluga whales live in Alaska"
    },
    {
      "start": 235.07,
      "end": 235.61,
      "text": "Oh"
    },
    {
      "start": 235.61,
      "end": 237.15,
      "text": "That's the only state they're found in"
    },
    {
      "start": 237.15,
      "end": 237.61,
      "text": "There"
    },
    {
      "start": 237.61,
      "end": 240.93,
      "text": "And they are critically endangered over there"
    },
    {
      "start": 240.93,
      "end": 241.23,
      "text": "Oh"
    },
    {
      "start": 241.23,
      "end": 243.01,
      "text": "Especially in the Cook Inlet"
    },
    {
      "start": 243.01,
      "end": 243.29,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 243.29,
      "end": 245.75,
      "text": "This water off the coast of Alaska"
    },
    {
      "start": 245.75,
      "end": 246.23,
      "text": "Oh"
    },
    {
      "start": 246.23,
      "end": 248.39,
      "text": "Many of the native Alaskans"
    },
    {
      "start": 248.39,
      "end": 248.65,
      "text": "Uh-huh"
    },
    {
      "start": 248.65,
      "end": 250.27,
      "text": "They hunted these whales"
    },
    {
      "start": 250.27,
      "end": 251.39,
      "text": "For food"
    },
    {
      "start": 251.39,
      "end": 252.03,
      "text": "Seriously"
    },
    {
      "start": 252.03,
      "end": 253.13,
      "text": "They lived off them"
    },
    {
      "start": 253.13,
      "end": 253.53,
      "text": "Uh-huh"
    },
    {
      "start": 253.53,
      "end": 255.85,
      "text": "And they also made many products with them"
    },
    {
      "start": 255.85,
      "end": 256.21,
      "text": "Oh"
    },
    {
      "start": 256.21,
      "end": 257.49,
      "text": "So that was one reason"
    },
    {
      "start": 257.49,
      "end": 258.55,
      "text": "Also oil"
    },
    {
      "start": 258.55,
      "end": 260.81,
      "text": "They get a lot of oil from Alaska"
    },
    {
      "start": 260.81,
      "end": 262.01,
      "text": "Oil spills"
    },
    {
      "start": 262.01,
      "end": 262.25,
      "text": "네"
    },
    {
      "start": 262.25,
      "end": 263.25,
      "text": "Chemicals"
    },
    {
      "start": 263.25,
      "end": 264.75,
      "text": "Can really hurt the water"
    },
    {
      "start": 264.75,
      "end": 265.69,
      "text": "So"
    },
    {
      "start": 265.69,
      "end": 268.53,
      "text": "They are on a critically endangered list"
    },
    {
      "start": 268.53,
      "end": 269.85,
      "text": "By the United States"
    },
    {
      "start": 269.85,
      "end": 271.09,
      "text": "And now they're protected"
    },
    {
      "start": 271.09,
      "end": 272.47,
      "text": "In Alaska"
    },
    {
      "start": 272.47,
      "end": 273.77,
      "text": "So hopefully"
    },
    {
      "start": 273.77,
      "end": 275.41,
      "text": "They are multiplying"
    },
    {
      "start": 275.41,
      "end": 276.15,
      "text": "And"
    },
    {
      "start": 276.15,
      "end": 277.51,
      "text": "자식 농사 잘"
    },
    {
      "start": 277.51,
      "end": 278.93,
      "text": "짓고 있을 거라고"
    },
    {
      "start": 278.93,
      "end": 279.77,
      "text": "맞습니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 279.77,
      "end": 281.01,
      "text": "심지어"
    },
    {
      "start": 281.01,
      "end": 282.09,
      "text": "우리가 알다시피"
    },
    {
      "start": 282.09,
      "end": 283.29,
      "text": "그 판다들도"
    },
    {
      "start": 283.29,
      "end": 284.27,
      "text": "마찬가지로"
    },
    {
      "start": 284.27,
      "end": 286.81,
      "text": "We're also at risk of extinction"
    },
    {
      "start": 286.81,
      "end": 288.91,
      "text": "의 상태에 있었다가"
    },
    {
      "start": 288.91,
      "end": 289.71,
      "text": "Major risk"
    },
    {
      "start": 289.71,
      "end": 291.55,
      "text": "But are now in vulnerable stage"
    },
    {
      "start": 291.55,
      "end": 292.31,
      "text": "가 되었잖아요"
    },
    {
      "start": 292.31,
      "end": 292.95,
      "text": "Vulnerable"
    },
    {
      "start": 292.95,
      "end": 293.83,
      "text": "So still"
    },
    {
      "start": 293.83,
      "end": 295.57,
      "text": "Not safe"
    },
    {
      "start": 295.57,
      "end": 296.05,
      "text": "그렇죠"
    },
    {
      "start": 296.05,
      "end": 297.45,
      "text": "그래도 조금씩 조금씩"
    },
    {
      "start": 297.45,
      "end": 298.33,
      "text": "나아지는 거라고"
    },
    {
      "start": 298.33,
      "end": 299.55,
      "text": "기대를 하게 한단 말이죠"
    },
    {
      "start": 299.55,
      "end": 300.21,
      "text": "Getting better"
    },
    {
      "start": 300.21,
      "end": 301.79,
      "text": "이처럼 우리가 좀"
    },
    {
      "start": 301.79,
      "end": 302.95,
      "text": "To protect"
    },
    {
      "start": 302.95,
      "end": 303.85,
      "text": "Belugas"
    },
    {
      "start": 303.85,
      "end": 304.53,
      "text": "를 하기 위해서"
    },
    {
      "start": 304.53,
      "end": 305.95,
      "text": "계속해서 좋은"
    },
    {
      "start": 305.95,
      "end": 307.05,
      "text": "방안에 대해서"
    },
    {
      "start": 307.05,
      "end": 307.99,
      "text": "연구하고"
    },
    {
      "start": 307.99,
      "end": 309.05,
      "text": "보호하기 위해서"
    },
    {
      "start": 309.05,
      "end": 309.87,
      "text": "노력을 한다면"
    },
    {
      "start": 309.87,
      "end": 311.39,
      "text": "좀 좋아지지 않을까"
    },
    {
      "start": 311.39,
      "end": 312.63,
      "text": "Because we need Belugas"
    },
    {
      "start": 312.63,
      "end": 314.53,
      "text": "They actually help clean the ocean"
    },
    {
      "start": 314.53,
      "end": 316.29,
      "text": "Like all the dead carcasses"
    },
    {
      "start": 316.29,
      "end": 317.61,
      "text": "And the weird things"
    },
    {
      "start": 317.61,
      "end": 318.47,
      "text": "They eat those"
    },
    {
      "start": 318.47,
      "end": 319.81,
      "text": "So they make the ocean"
    },
    {
      "start": 319.81,
      "end": 321.45,
      "text": "a cleaner and happier place"
    },
    {
      "start": 321.45,
      "end": 322.79,
      "text": "We need the Belugas"
    },
    {
      "start": 322.79,
      "end": 323.09,
      "text": "네"
    },
    {
      "start": 323.09,
      "end": 324.73,
      "text": "이렇게 같이 살아가는"
    },
    {
      "start": 324.73,
      "end": 325.75,
      "text": "그런 지구가 되면"
    },
    {
      "start": 325.75,
      "end": 326.75,
      "text": "너무너무 좋겠습니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 326.75,
      "end": 328.53,
      "text": "그러면 오늘 준비된 장면"
    },
    {
      "start": 328.53,
      "end": 329.25,
      "text": "듣고 오시죠"
    },
    {
      "start": 329.25,
      "end": 332.53,
      "text": "Well as of right now"
    },
    {
      "start": 332.53,
      "end": 333.91,
      "text": "there's no denying it"
    },
    {
      "start": 333.91,
      "end": 335.47,
      "text": "we're on the brink of extinction"
    },
    {
      "start": 335.47,
      "end": 337.56,
      "text": "and pretty soon"
    },
    {
      "start": 337.56,
      "end": 338.94,
      "text": "there won't be one Beluga"
    },
    {
      "start": 338.94,
      "end": 339.84,
      "text": "left in the river"
    },
    {
      "start": 339.84,
      "end": 340.84,
      "text": "If only we knew"
    },
    {
      "start": 340.84,
      "end": 342.66,
      "text": "why it was happening to us"
    },
    {
      "start": 342.66,
      "end": 343.56,
      "text": "It was the noise"
    },
    {
      "start": 343.56,
      "end": 344.72,
      "text": "that stressed out Estelle"
    },
    {
      "start": 344.72,
      "end": 345.66,
      "text": "That's true"
    },
    {
      "start": 345.66,
      "end": 346.96,
      "text": "before it was a lot quieter"
    },
    {
      "start": 346.96,
      "end": 347.76,
      "text": "Does that mean"
    },
    {
      "start": 347.76,
      "end": 348.78,
      "text": "we'll have to move"
    },
    {
      "start": 348.78,
      "end": 350.1,
      "text": "if it gets too noisy?"
    },
    {
      "start": 350.26,
      "end": 351.38,
      "text": "But where would we go?"
    },
    {
      "start": 351.7,
      "end": 352.66,
      "text": "Grandma and Old Nick"
    },
    {
      "start": 352.66,
      "end": 354.22,
      "text": "are too old to move now"
    },
    {
      "start": 354.22,
      "end": 356.36,
      "text": "You'll just have to leave me here"
    },
    {
      "start": 356.36,
      "end": 357.48,
      "text": "Me as well"
    },
    {
      "start": 357.48,
      "end": 359.42,
      "text": "Oh"
    },
    {
      "start": 359.42,
      "end": 360.38,
      "text": "Who is that?"
    },
    {
      "start": 360.38,
      "end": 362.32,
      "text": "성우의 목소리를 듣고"
    },
    {
      "start": 362.32,
      "end": 363.84,
      "text": "웃음을 참을 수가 없었어요"
    },
    {
      "start": 363.84,
      "end": 364.84,
      "text": "누구시지?"
    },
    {
      "start": 364.96,
      "end": 366.2,
      "text": "이거 하실 수 있겠어요?"
    },
    {
      "start": 366.32,
      "end": 367.04,
      "text": "못하겠어요"
    },
    {
      "start": 367.04,
      "end": 369.42,
      "text": "지금 상황은"
    },
    {
      "start": 369.42,
      "end": 370.82,
      "text": "되게 심각한 상황이었어요"
    },
    {
      "start": 370.82,
      "end": 372.98,
      "text": "A very serious situation"
    },
    {
      "start": 372.98,
      "end": 373.32,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 373.32,
      "end": 374.5,
      "text": "They're aware of"
    },
    {
      "start": 374.5,
      "end": 375.76,
      "text": "the problem"
    },
    {
      "start": 375.76,
      "end": 377.7,
      "text": "특히 환경적으로"
    },
    {
      "start": 377.7,
      "end": 379.74,
      "text": "그들이 처한 문제에 대해서"
    },
    {
      "start": 379.74,
      "end": 381.68,
      "text": "Beluga들도 심지어"
    },
    {
      "start": 381.68,
      "end": 383.7,
      "text": "스스로 자각을 하고 있는 상황입니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 383.7,
      "end": 384.04,
      "text": "Wow"
    },
    {
      "start": 384.04,
      "end": 384.98,
      "text": "Even they know"
    },
    {
      "start": 384.98,
      "end": 386.26,
      "text": "The whales themselves"
    },
    {
      "start": 386.26,
      "end": 388.86,
      "text": "know they're on the brink of extinction"
    },
    {
      "start": 388.86,
      "end": 389.36,
      "text": "그렇죠"
    },
    {
      "start": 389.36,
      "end": 390.32,
      "text": "Dangerous"
    },
    {
      "start": 390.32,
      "end": 391.12,
      "text": "특히"
    },
    {
      "start": 391.12,
      "end": 392.8,
      "text": "In the Arctic에서"
    },
    {
      "start": 392.8,
      "end": 396.54,
      "text": "큰 대형 배들이 지나가면서도"
    },
    {
      "start": 396.54,
      "end": 396.82,
      "text": "even"
    },
    {
      "start": 396.82,
      "end": 398.02,
      "text": "red glaciers"
    },
    {
      "start": 398.02,
      "end": 398.68,
      "text": "할 수 있잖아요"
    },
    {
      "start": 398.68,
      "end": 399.9,
      "text": "Those huge cargo ships"
    },
    {
      "start": 399.9,
      "end": 400.32,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 400.32,
      "end": 402.24,
      "text": "Like the one that hit that bridge"
    },
    {
      "start": 402.24,
      "end": 403.12,
      "text": "in Baltimore"
    },
    {
      "start": 403.12,
      "end": 404.0,
      "text": "recently"
    },
    {
      "start": 404.0,
      "end": 406.32,
      "text": "Gigantic container ships"
    },
    {
      "start": 406.32,
      "end": 408.68,
      "text": "Those can be a threat to whales"
    },
    {
      "start": 408.68,
      "end": 414.18,
      "text": "이렇게 어떤 환경의 사고로 인하여"
    },
    {
      "start": 414.18,
      "end": 416.74,
      "text": "이 동물들이 위기에 처할 수도 있겠네요"
    },
    {
      "start": 416.74,
      "end": 417.12,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 417.12,
      "end": 418.52,
      "text": "It's like us people"
    },
    {
      "start": 418.52,
      "end": 419.46,
      "text": "We're thinking"
    },
    {
      "start": 419.46,
      "end": 421.68,
      "text": "When the earth is gonna end"
    },
    {
      "start": 421.68,
      "end": 423.54,
      "text": "Should we go live on Mars?"
    },
    {
      "start": 423.76,
      "end": 425.14,
      "text": "And people like Elon Musk"
    },
    {
      "start": 425.14,
      "end": 426.82,
      "text": "are trying to make plans"
    },
    {
      "start": 426.82,
      "end": 427.12,
      "text": "그렇죠"
    },
    {
      "start": 427.12,
      "end": 428.62,
      "text": "So animals"
    },
    {
      "start": 428.62,
      "end": 430.94,
      "text": "have been in the same predicament"
    },
    {
      "start": 430.94,
      "end": 432.46,
      "text": "for a long, long time"
    },
    {
      "start": 432.46,
      "end": 434.62,
      "text": "그래서 이 친구들도"
    },
    {
      "start": 434.62,
      "end": 436.62,
      "text": "인간처럼 비슷하게"
    },
    {
      "start": 436.62,
      "end": 438.2,
      "text": "우리 어디로 가야 하는 거야"
    },
    {
      "start": 438.2,
      "end": 440.38,
      "text": "막 이렇게 고민을 하고 있는 상황이었어요"
    },
    {
      "start": 440.38,
      "end": 442.46,
      "text": "일단은 주요 표현들 살펴볼까요?"
    },
    {
      "start": 442.68,
      "end": 444.34,
      "text": "There's no denying it"
    },
    {
      "start": 444.34,
      "end": 446.18,
      "text": "부인할 수가 없다"
    },
    {
      "start": 446.18,
      "end": 447.9,
      "text": "No, I'm not"
    },
    {
      "start": 447.9,
      "end": 449.16,
      "text": "There's no denying it"
    },
    {
      "start": 449.16,
      "end": 450.22,
      "text": "No, I'm not ugly"
    },
    {
      "start": 450.22,
      "end": 451.36,
      "text": "Come on"
    },
    {
      "start": 451.36,
      "end": 452.52,
      "text": "Oh, yes"
    },
    {
      "start": 452.52,
      "end": 454.68,
      "text": "아, 예가 정말 와닿네요"
    },
    {
      "start": 454.68,
      "end": 456.3,
      "text": "어릴 때 추억"
    },
    {
      "start": 456.3,
      "end": 459.22,
      "text": "On the brink of extinction"
    },
    {
      "start": 459.22,
      "end": 460.68,
      "text": "아, on the brink"
    },
    {
      "start": 460.68,
      "end": 461.52,
      "text": "brink네요"
    },
    {
      "start": 461.52,
      "end": 464.4,
      "text": "On the brink of extinction"
    },
    {
      "start": 464.4,
      "end": 466.44,
      "text": "멸종 직전에"
    },
    {
      "start": 466.44,
      "end": 467.56,
      "text": "라는 의미입니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 467.56,
      "end": 468.36,
      "text": "On the brink of"
    },
    {
      "start": 468.36,
      "end": 469.46,
      "text": "On the brink of sanity"
    },
    {
      "start": 469.46,
      "end": 470.84,
      "text": "On the brink of hunger"
    },
    {
      "start": 470.84,
      "end": 471.78,
      "text": "On the brink of"
    },
    {
      "start": 471.78,
      "end": 472.5,
      "text": "그 경계선"
    },
    {
      "start": 472.5,
      "end": 473.88,
      "text": "아, 그런 많은 것들이 있죠"
    },
    {
      "start": 473.88,
      "end": 478.28,
      "text": "It was noise that stressed out Estelle"
    },
    {
      "start": 478.28,
      "end": 480.88,
      "text": "아, Estelle 하니까 기억이 납니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 480.88,
      "end": 482.04,
      "text": "Estelle, who's Estelle?"
    },
    {
      "start": 482.2,
      "end": 485.24,
      "text": "지난번에 그 큰 어선이 지나가면서"
    },
    {
      "start": 485.24,
      "end": 487.62,
      "text": "Estelle이 다칠 뻔했어요"
    },
    {
      "start": 487.62,
      "end": 490.44,
      "text": "Oh, almost got hit by that big ship"
    },
    {
      "start": 490.44,
      "end": 490.72,
      "text": "Right"
    },
    {
      "start": 490.72,
      "end": 492.28,
      "text": "It was saved at the last moment"
    },
    {
      "start": 492.28,
      "end": 494.36,
      "text": "So, it was noise"
    },
    {
      "start": 494.36,
      "end": 495.5,
      "text": "소음이었어"
    },
    {
      "start": 495.5,
      "end": 497.2,
      "text": "That stressed out Estelle"
    },
    {
      "start": 497.2,
      "end": 500.58,
      "text": "Estelle한테 스트레스를 준 것은 소음이었다"
    },
    {
      "start": 500.58,
      "end": 501.5,
      "text": "아, 맞다"
    },
    {
      "start": 501.5,
      "end": 502.96,
      "text": "The ships make some noise"
    },
    {
      "start": 502.96,
      "end": 505.96,
      "text": "And it interferes with the whale's communication"
    },
    {
      "start": 505.96,
      "end": 506.34,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 506.34,
      "end": 507.26,
      "text": "So, they can't"
    },
    {
      "start": 507.26,
      "end": 508.36,
      "text": "They don't know where to go"
    },
    {
      "start": 508.36,
      "end": 509.98,
      "text": "And 막 헤매고 있더라고"
    },
    {
      "start": 509.98,
      "end": 510.48,
      "text": "맞아요"
    },
    {
      "start": 510.48,
      "end": 511.26,
      "text": "Oh, 뭐"
    },
    {
      "start": 511.26,
      "end": 514.02,
      "text": "이 멜로가들이 귀를 막고 있는"
    },
    {
      "start": 514.02,
      "end": 515.76,
      "text": "그런 장면들도 보였습니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 515.76,
      "end": 518.08,
      "text": "그러면 이 내용 한 번 더 들어보시죠"
    },
    {
      "start": 518.08,
      "end": 521.54,
      "text": "Well, as of right now"
    },
    {
      "start": 521.54,
      "end": 522.92,
      "text": "There's no denying it"
    },
    {
      "start": 522.92,
      "end": 524.5,
      "text": "We're on the brink of extinction"
    },
    {
      "start": 524.5,
      "end": 526.59,
      "text": "And pretty soon"
    },
    {
      "start": 526.59,
      "end": 528.85,
      "text": "There won't be one beluga left in the river"
    },
    {
      "start": 528.85,
      "end": 531.67,
      "text": "If only we knew why it was happening to us"
    },
    {
      "start": 531.67,
      "end": 533.73,
      "text": "It was the noise that stressed out Estelle"
    },
    {
      "start": 533.73,
      "end": 534.67,
      "text": "That's true"
    },
    {
      "start": 534.67,
      "end": 535.97,
      "text": "Before it was a lot quieter"
    },
    {
      "start": 535.97,
      "end": 537.77,
      "text": "Does that mean we'll have to move"
    },
    {
      "start": 537.77,
      "end": 539.09,
      "text": "If it gets too noisy"
    },
    {
      "start": 539.09,
      "end": 540.39,
      "text": "But where would we go"
    },
    {
      "start": 540.39,
      "end": 543.23,
      "text": "Grandma and old neck are too old to move now"
    },
    {
      "start": 543.23,
      "end": 545.35,
      "text": "You'll just have to leave me here"
    },
    {
      "start": 545.35,
      "end": 547.78,
      "text": "Me as well"
    },
    {
      "start": 547.78,
      "end": 549.62,
      "text": "네, 자, Estelle"
    },
    {
      "start": 549.62,
      "end": 553.96,
      "text": "그때 다칠 뻔한 기억이 다시 한 번 떠오를 것 같습니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 553.96,
      "end": 556.34,
      "text": "지금도 트라우마 때문에 고생을 하고 있더라고요"
    },
    {
      "start": 556.34,
      "end": 558.36,
      "text": "PSTD라고 하죠?"
    },
    {
      "start": 558.76,
      "end": 560.1,
      "text": "PSTD 있는 것 같아요"
    },
    {
      "start": 560.1,
      "end": 564.22,
      "text": "네, 그럼 이제 보스코라는 친구가 하는 말부터 확인해 볼까요?"
    },
    {
      "start": 564.22,
      "end": 565.64,
      "text": "남자죠"
    },
    {
      "start": 565.64,
      "end": 568.26,
      "text": "Well, as of right now"
    },
    {
      "start": 568.26,
      "end": 570.1,
      "text": "There's no denying it"
    },
    {
      "start": 570.1,
      "end": 572.0,
      "text": "이제는 말이야"
    },
    {
      "start": 572.0,
      "end": 573.64,
      "text": "There's no denying it"
    },
    {
      "start": 573.64,
      "end": 575.44,
      "text": "더 이상 부인할 수가 없어"
    },
    {
      "start": 575.44,
      "end": 577.94,
      "text": "We're on the brink of extinction"
    },
    {
      "start": 577.94,
      "end": 579.52,
      "text": "And pretty soon"
    },
    {
      "start": 579.52,
      "end": 582.52,
      "text": "There won't be one beluga left in the river"
    },
    {
      "start": 582.52,
      "end": 586.96,
      "text": "우리 beluga는 멸종 직전에 있어"
    },
    {
      "start": 586.96,
      "end": 588.38,
      "text": "And pretty soon"
    },
    {
      "start": 588.38,
      "end": 590.06,
      "text": "그리고 곧 머지않아"
    },
    {
      "start": 590.06,
      "end": 593.2,
      "text": "There won't be one beluga left in the river"
    },
    {
      "start": 593.2,
      "end": 597.54,
      "text": "이 강에 단 한 마리의 beluga도 남지 않을 거야"
    },
    {
      "start": 597.54,
      "end": 601.82,
      "text": "If only we knew why it was happening to us"
    },
    {
      "start": 601.82,
      "end": 603.34,
      "text": "It's perfect"
    },
    {
      "start": 603.34,
      "end": 604.3,
      "text": "Really?"
    },
    {
      "start": 604.56,
      "end": 604.84,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 604.84,
      "end": 605.62,
      "text": "Thank you"
    },
    {
      "start": 605.62,
      "end": 606.78,
      "text": "예상하지 못했어요"
    },
    {
      "start": 606.78,
      "end": 608.0,
      "text": "이렇게 똑같이 하실 줄이야"
    },
    {
      "start": 608.0,
      "end": 608.86,
      "text": "고맙다"
    },
    {
      "start": 608.86,
      "end": 611.12,
      "text": "전혀 더 나쁘지 않네"
    },
    {
      "start": 611.12,
      "end": 615.32,
      "text": "네, 할아버지 목소리에 아주 탁월한 연기력을 갖추고 계십니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 615.32,
      "end": 616.12,
      "text": "고맙다"
    },
    {
      "start": 616.12,
      "end": 620.38,
      "text": "If only we knew why it was happening to us"
    },
    {
      "start": 620.38,
      "end": 621.38,
      "text": "이렇게 들으셨는데요"
    },
    {
      "start": 621.38,
      "end": 624.72,
      "text": "우리에게 왜 이런 일이 생긴 걸까"
    },
    {
      "start": 624.72,
      "end": 626.52,
      "text": "라고 해석을 할 수가 있겠네요"
    },
    {
      "start": 626.52,
      "end": 629.44,
      "text": "특히 if only 라고 시작을 했으니까"
    },
    {
      "start": 629.44,
      "end": 631.08,
      "text": "뭐뭐이면 좋을 텐데"
    },
    {
      "start": 631.08,
      "end": 635.12,
      "text": "이런 일이 우리에게 도대체 왜 발생했는지"
    },
    {
      "start": 635.12,
      "end": 636.72,
      "text": "안다면 참 좋을 텐데"
    },
    {
      "start": 636.72,
      "end": 639.02,
      "text": "If only that"
    },
    {
      "start": 639.02,
      "end": 640.14,
      "text": "할아버지 거래"
    },
    {
      "start": 640.14,
      "end": 642.48,
      "text": "If only that 할아버지 did not run away"
    },
    {
      "start": 642.48,
      "end": 644.72,
      "text": "We would have lived happily ever after"
    },
    {
      "start": 644.72,
      "end": 647.86,
      "text": "이렇게 응용 문장까지도 만드실 수 있겠네요"
    },
    {
      "start": 647.86,
      "end": 650.88,
      "text": "그 다음 여성 암컷이죠"
    },
    {
      "start": 650.88,
      "end": 652.26,
      "text": "모르겠어요"
    },
    {
      "start": 652.26,
      "end": 652.92,
      "text": "암컷일 거예요"
    },
    {
      "start": 652.92,
      "end": 654.06,
      "text": "암컷 맞을 거예요"
    },
    {
      "start": 654.06,
      "end": 655.5,
      "text": "맞다고 쳐요"
    },
    {
      "start": 655.5,
      "end": 659.06,
      "text": "It was noise that stressed out Estelle"
    },
    {
      "start": 659.06,
      "end": 663.26,
      "text": "아, 에스텔에게 스트레스를 준 건 소음이었어요"
    },
    {
      "start": 663.26,
      "end": 664.4,
      "text": "That's true"
    },
    {
      "start": 664.4,
      "end": 666.6,
      "text": "Before it was a lot quieter"
    },
    {
      "start": 666.6,
      "end": 667.96,
      "text": "그래, 맞아"
    },
    {
      "start": 667.96,
      "end": 669.9,
      "text": "저는 훨씬 더 조용했는데"
    },
    {
      "start": 669.9,
      "end": 672.02,
      "text": "Does that mean"
    },
    {
      "start": 672.02,
      "end": 675.26,
      "text": "we'll have to move if it gets too noisy?"
    },
    {
      "start": 675.42,
      "end": 677.7,
      "text": "아, 그 할아버지 거래가 다시 등장을 했습니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 677.7,
      "end": 679.62,
      "text": "Does that mean"
    },
    {
      "start": 679.62,
      "end": 682.96,
      "text": "we'll have to move if it gets too noisy?"
    },
    {
      "start": 683.52,
      "end": 686.5,
      "text": "그럼 더 시끄러워지면 다른 곳으로 가야 하는 거예요?"
    },
    {
      "start": 687.06,
      "end": 688.32,
      "text": "But where would we go?"
    },
    {
      "start": 688.32,
      "end": 691.39,
      "text": "But where would we go?"
    },
    {
      "start": 691.79,
      "end": 693.29,
      "text": "우리가 어디로 갈 수 있겠어?"
    },
    {
      "start": 694.01,
      "end": 697.17,
      "text": "Grandma and old Nick are too old to move now"
    },
    {
      "start": 697.17,
      "end": 700.27,
      "text": "할머니랑 그리고 old Nick"
    },
    {
      "start": 700.27,
      "end": 702.09,
      "text": "이 old Nick 할아버지는"
    },
    {
      "start": 702.09,
      "end": 704.73,
      "text": "are too old to move now"
    },
    {
      "start": 704.73,
      "end": 706.99,
      "text": "지금 어딘가 이동하기에는"
    },
    {
      "start": 706.99,
      "end": 708.73,
      "text": "너무 나이 드셨어"
    },
    {
      "start": 708.73,
      "end": 711.87,
      "text": "You'll just have to leave me here"
    },
    {
      "start": 711.87,
      "end": 713.59,
      "text": "좀 슬프네요"
    },
    {
      "start": 713.59,
      "end": 715.37,
      "text": "할아버지가 이야기하신 겁니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 715.37,
      "end": 717.87,
      "text": "You'll just have to leave me here"
    },
    {
      "start": 717.87,
      "end": 721.01,
      "text": "나는 그냥 여기 남아있으면 돼"
    },
    {
      "start": 721.01,
      "end": 722.85,
      "text": "Me too"
    },
    {
      "start": 722.85,
      "end": 725.41,
      "text": "Me as well"
    },
    {
      "start": 725.41,
      "end": 726.39,
      "text": "할머니죠?"
    },
    {
      "start": 726.43,
      "end": 727.51,
      "text": "할머니였어요"
    },
    {
      "start": 727.51,
      "end": 728.91,
      "text": "Me as well"
    },
    {
      "start": 728.91,
      "end": 730.55,
      "text": "나도 마찬가지야"
    },
    {
      "start": 730.55,
      "end": 732.19,
      "text": "나도 여기에 두고 가렴"
    },
    {
      "start": 732.19,
      "end": 734.33,
      "text": "이렇게 대화를 나누고 있습니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 734.33,
      "end": 736.03,
      "text": "They're going to sacrifice"
    },
    {
      "start": 736.03,
      "end": 737.31,
      "text": "for the team"
    },
    {
      "start": 737.31,
      "end": 738.59,
      "text": "That's sad"
    },
    {
      "start": 738.59,
      "end": 738.97,
      "text": "Come on"
    },
    {
      "start": 738.97,
      "end": 740.15,
      "text": "You got to take them with you"
    },
    {
      "start": 740.15,
      "end": 741.67,
      "text": "어르신들 모시고 가야죠"
    },
    {
      "start": 741.67,
      "end": 744.69,
      "text": "참 멀는데 큰일 났네요"
    },
    {
      "start": 744.69,
      "end": 748.77,
      "text": "어떻게 열심히 건강관리를 시켜드려야 될 것 같습니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 748.77,
      "end": 749.25,
      "text": "아 네"
    },
    {
      "start": 749.25,
      "end": 750.63,
      "text": "감기식 챙겨 드시고"
    },
    {
      "start": 750.63,
      "end": 755.4,
      "text": "그럼 마지막으로 한 번 더 확인해 보시죠"
    },
    {
      "start": 755.4,
      "end": 757.1,
      "text": "Well, as of right now"
    },
    {
      "start": 757.1,
      "end": 758.46,
      "text": "there's no denying it"
    },
    {
      "start": 758.46,
      "end": 760.06,
      "text": "We're on the brink of extinction"
    },
    {
      "start": 760.06,
      "end": 762.14,
      "text": "And pretty soon"
    },
    {
      "start": 762.14,
      "end": 764.42,
      "text": "there won't be one beluga left in the river"
    },
    {
      "start": 764.42,
      "end": 765.64,
      "text": "If only we knew why"
    },
    {
      "start": 765.64,
      "end": 767.24,
      "text": "it was happening to us"
    },
    {
      "start": 767.24,
      "end": 769.28,
      "text": "It was the noise that stressed out Estelle"
    },
    {
      "start": 769.28,
      "end": 770.22,
      "text": "That's true"
    },
    {
      "start": 770.22,
      "end": 771.52,
      "text": "Before it was a lot quieter"
    },
    {
      "start": 771.52,
      "end": 773.32,
      "text": "Does that mean we'll have to move"
    },
    {
      "start": 773.32,
      "end": 774.66,
      "text": "if it gets too noisy?"
    },
    {
      "start": 774.8,
      "end": 775.94,
      "text": "But where would we go?"
    },
    {
      "start": 776.26,
      "end": 777.24,
      "text": "Grandma and old Nick"
    },
    {
      "start": 777.24,
      "end": 778.78,
      "text": "are too old to move now"
    },
    {
      "start": 778.78,
      "end": 780.9,
      "text": "You'll just have to leave me here"
    },
    {
      "start": 780.9,
      "end": 782.06,
      "text": "Me as well"
    },
    {
      "start": 782.06,
      "end": 786.07,
      "text": "최혜준님께서 메시지 주셨는데요"
    },
    {
      "start": 786.07,
      "end": 788.77,
      "text": "이번 주즉부터 듣기 시작했는데"
    },
    {
      "start": 788.77,
      "end": 790.81,
      "text": "Screen English 너무 재밌어요"
    }
  ]
}